{"tid":1795741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(國際戰線) GTA V更新疑似香港示威者裝備觸發中港玩家對抗","createTime":"2019-12-24T06:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T09:15:21.000Z","uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"331ef4ee166e248cb765a709c3be6fead73f111b","tid":1795741,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:45:55.000Z","msg":"GTA V更新疑似香港示威者裝備觸發中港玩家對抗<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】反修例風波爆發逾半年，持不同意見的人士不時有磨擦發生。近日中港網民之間亦出現衝突，不過就是在電子遊戲的虛擬世界入面。電子遊戲「俠盜獵車手五」GTA V月初的一次更新，引起中港玩家的「大戰」。<br />\n<br />\n《英國廣播公司》報道，事緣在GTA V在12月12日的更新中，加入大量新的衣著供玩家選擇，當中包括黃色安全帽、「豬嘴」防毒面罩等，與現實中香港示威者的裝備不謀而合。<br />\n<br />\n有關消息在網上討論區「連登」傳開後，有香港玩家更開設名叫「Stand with Hong Kong」的公會，聚眾在遊戲中破壞鐵路設施和攻擊警車。有內地玩家就穿上類似防暴警察的裝束，並駕駛水炮車在遊戲中與香港玩家對抗。<br />\n<br />\n報道指雙方展開「激戰」，內地玩家宣稱在人數優勢下獲勝。<br />\n<br />\n不過其實GTA V在內地並無獲得官方批准發售，因為當局指遊戲含有毒品、暴力和色情內容，內地玩家只能使用個別平台下載，並透過監控漏洞連接遊戲的伺服器。"},{"pid":"a3c339ea95243bdad360c459ec1e3b292219ce13","tid":1795741,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:46:58.000Z","msg":"內地玩家只能使用個別平台下載，並透過監控漏洞連接遊戲的伺服器。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67d8af3a66f5c661fbae9653eff89b7ea23c8c0","tid":1795741,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"支那豬玩GTA姐係唔愛黨<br />\n坦克直接開出來"},{"pid":"0aaa700da24e9be3c41c1da5239cf55352f59a65","tid":1795741,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:49:15.000Z","msg":"入去打過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa44eb8c6a5b1fabefa7689b2d07b38084ecfe95","tid":1795741,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f389cfaffd29b6402fe7f7abcb1ae50d4467068","tid":1795741,"uid":126649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"聚眾在遊戲中破壞鐵路設施和攻擊警車。有內地玩家就穿上類似防暴警察的裝束，並駕駛水炮車在遊戲中與香港玩家對抗。<br />\n<br />\nWTF?"},{"pid":"bea01269e269ebe5825379fbd7d1e1cfdbe8f768","tid":1795741,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84f35a97254144e4f902b9e6621481ed268d873","tid":1795741,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3c339ea95243bdad360c459ec1e3b292219ce13","tid":1795741,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:46:58.000Z","msg":"內地玩家只能使用個別平台下載，並透過監控漏洞連接遊戲的伺服器。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係犯法都要拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a320393d396bb7a65e3ecb7f5b6db3ecca91ca4","tid":1795741,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6b0e8b9783db9a2303d33935d79e7d10e18e10","tid":1795741,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"有無片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8de2079b3987a5662d96198cf484e6d67eb7dc2","tid":1795741,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed044846d4cfaf10eee1ab736b3bdc3687ec82b","tid":1795741,"uid":259569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:57:17.000Z","msg":"笑死 支那豬又打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e820a521e4a8992876cc7ba5b81974b062f5f51c","tid":1795741,"uid":209422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9